__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    listWallets:
      path: /wallets
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
      display-name: List wallets
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: list<Wallet>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              - id: id
                balance: 1.1
                currency: currency
                createdAt: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
    getWallet:
      path: /wallets/{walletId}
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
      path-parameters:
        walletId: string
      display-name: Get wallet by ID
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: Wallet
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            walletId: walletId
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              balance: 1.1
              currency: currency
              createdAt: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
    getWalletBalance:
      path: /wallets/{walletId}/balance
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
      path-parameters:
        walletId: string
      display-name: Get wallet balance
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: Balance
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            walletId: walletId
          response:
            body:
              available: 1.1
              pending: 1.1
              currency: currency
    listAccounts:
      path: /accounts
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
      display-name: List accounts
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: list<Account>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              - id: id
                name: name
                type: checking
    listTransactions:
      path: /transactions
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../payments-api.yml
      display-name: List transactions
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: list<Transaction>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              - id: id
                amount: 1.1
                currency: currency
                status: pending
                timestamp: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
    getTransaction:
      path: /transactions/{transactionId}
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../payments-api.yml
      path-parameters:
        transactionId: string
      display-name: Get transaction by ID
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: Transaction
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            transactionId: transactionId
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              amount: 1.1
              currency: currency
              status: pending
              timestamp: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
    createPayment:
      path: /payments
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../payments-api.yml
      display-name: Create a payment
      request:
        name: PaymentRequest
        body:
          properties:
            amount: double
            currency: string
            recipient: string
            description: optional<string>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: PaymentResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            amount: 1.1
            currency: currency
            recipient: recipient
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              status: accepted
              message: message
    refundPayment:
      path: /payments/{paymentId}/refund
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../payments-api.yml
      path-parameters:
        paymentId: string
      display-name: Refund a payment
      request:
        name: RefundRequest
        body:
          properties:
            amount: double
            reason: optional<string>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: RefundResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            paymentId: paymentId
          request:
            amount: 1.1
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              status: pending
              refundedAmount: 1.1
    listRefunds:
      path: /refunds
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../payments-api.yml
      display-name: List all refunds
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: list<Refund>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              - id: id
                paymentId: paymentId
                amount: 1.1
                status: pending
                createdAt: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
  source:
    openapi: ../payments-api.yml
types:
  Wallet:
    properties:
      id: string
      balance: double
      currency: string
      createdAt: datetime
    source:
      openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
  Balance:
    properties:
      available: double
      pending: double
      currency: string
    source:
      openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
  AccountType:
    enum:
      - checking
      - savings
      - credit
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
  Account:
    properties:
      id: string
      name: string
      type: AccountType
    source:
      openapi: ../fintech-api.yml
  TransactionStatus:
    enum:
      - pending
      - completed
      - failed
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  Transaction:
    properties:
      id: string
      amount: double
      currency: string
      status: TransactionStatus
      timestamp: datetime
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  PaymentResponseStatus:
    enum:
      - accepted
      - rejected
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  PaymentResponse:
    properties:
      id: string
      status: PaymentResponseStatus
      message: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  RefundResponseStatus:
    enum:
      - pending
      - completed
      - failed
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  RefundResponse:
    properties:
      id: string
      status: RefundResponseStatus
      refundedAmount: double
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  RefundStatus:
    enum:
      - pending
      - completed
      - failed
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml
  Refund:
    properties:
      id: string
      paymentId: string
      amount: double
      status: RefundStatus
      createdAt: datetime
    source:
      openapi: ../payments-api.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Fintech API
environments:
  PRD: https://payments.api.example.com
  SBX: https://payments-sbx.api.example.com
  STG: https://payments-stg.api.example.com
  PRF: https://payments-prf.api.example.com
  E2E: https://payments-e2e.api.example.com
  QAL: https://payments-qal.api.example.com
default-environment: PRD
